---
title: Herby Chicken & Haloumi with Hummus Sauce, Garlic Rice & Cucumber Salad
description: This meal is all Mediterranean vibes, with spiced chicken and garlicky rice dressed in a fresh and tasty yoghurt
hummus. Accompanied by a crunchy cucumber salad and haloumi, every bite is a passport to sunny shores and savoury delights!
